10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Jasper is best suited for marketing teams, ad copy, brand voice content, campaigns, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. SEO.ai, meanwhile, shines for SEO optimized content, content scoring, keyword targeting, SEO teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2021, Jasper describes itself as \"Enterprise AI marketing platform for brand-consistent content.\" SEO.ai, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI-first SEO writing tool with real-time optimization scoring.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Jasper** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (10 vs 7). However, this does not mean SEO.ai is a poor choice — far from it. SEO.ai excels in its own right, particularly for SEO optimized content and content scoring.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value 50+ templates for marketing use cases, go with Jasper. If real-time seo scoring as you write matters more to you, SEO.ai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
